{"tid":614182,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人喺無鬧鐘叫醒既情況下會係固定時間起身","createTime":"2018-04-02T09:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T15:21:40.000Z","uid":58841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b01bffa219e695829c293fc155fe92b188749bee","tid":614182,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"即係我無論12點瞓又好2點定4點瞓都好<br />\n唔知點解就會好準時咁11點答1醒左<br />\n但係又瞓唔返<br />\n有冇人知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89895b42f05b6154b943e60f03df0dbcd1860295","tid":614182,"uid":172948,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"生理時鐘囉<br />\n其實仲有你可以每日固定時間屙屎"},{"pid":"5d1539f08e5e02edf8e6f725b9837a81830ca6a2","tid":614182,"uid":135123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:53:27.000Z","msg":"以前有段時間六七點食飯又冇食宵夜，朝朝七點肚餓醒"},{"pid":"58c4ce3f149658ba7247e996172a0968796a54fa","tid":614182,"uid":117679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工日子每日準時6點9。<br />\n放假每日準時8點鐘。<br />\n<br />\n屎一定返工前痾。<br />\n假期日子就一定朝早痾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2b9e8073d18c40ee76100cf05ed4551133a816","tid":614182,"uid":50856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"自動7,8點醒"},{"pid":"15230d08a32e87089987e08e565573100d97fdbb","tid":614182,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"星期六會自動好早醒左<br />\n慣左一至五早起"},{"pid":"11d434c079ff95962963909e65e6d76f82117ba1","tid":614182,"uid":64550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:27:51.000Z","msg":"發覺如果第2日有重要野做 可以變自動起身mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返工就鬧鐘響都唔想起 但係如果第2日有開心野做就會自動早鬧鐘時間半至1個鐘起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好神奇"},{"pid":"326327c85bf98ea05d0412f3566f9a2ab7a0ee98","tid":614182,"uid":64550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:28:51.000Z","msg":"原來有d off topic 眼殘左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc513b85b893160f3f5e240c9b0edaf5c3bcc767","tid":614182,"uid":67197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"每日6點自動起身返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星期日都係6點醒，之後訓返<br />\n呢4日假都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9eb2d29b708e1e3019d5b847938a4bb2e6443bb","tid":614182,"uid":27397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20876ceaf91cff93ca08a2081425c9adff29c25","tid":614182,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:21:40.000Z","msg":"你以前捱過夜？<br />\n我大學暑假時晚晚5點先瞓，用咗成個月先適應番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n初頭12點瞓晚晚3點會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁撚辛苦"}]}